Dependencies
------------
C++ compiler    (POSIX-compatible mobile device version)
libcurl         (statically compiled version for mobile device)
Xcode           (for iOS)
fruitstrap      (only for deploying an iOS app to an iOS device)
Android SDK     (for Android)

Build Instructions
------------------
Build hhms-lib:
	make

Build for iOS Simulator:
	make ios-simulator

Run on iOS Simulator
	make ios-simulator-run

Build for iOS Device:
	make ios-device

Install on iOS Device:
	make ios-device-install

Run on iOS Device (with attached debugger):
	make ios-device-run

